overview: When a pianist reaches world glory, he's usually exceptionally good at what he does. The way he handles the keys is unrivaled and he inspires awe in everyone watching.  Manuel Schenkhuizen is a pianist and his exceptional skills have to do with keys, but he doesn't use them on a piano. The keyboard is his instrument of choice. Manuel, known as Grubby to the gaming scene, is one of the best WarCraft players in the world. In our newest episode of /QRY, we visit the famous player in his home in the Netherlands, get to know his family and how he started his career.
title: QRY Grubby
